  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the silence of the night, the door creaks... You are an uninvited guest in a house that the owners have long since abandoned. But you are not alone here. A dark silhouette watches from the shadows, following your every step. Who is he? And why does this house not let go of those who cross its threshold?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore rooms full of secrets and terrible finds. Read the notes of the former owner, who tried to drive out the evil, but failed. Solve the riddles to finish what you started - or become the next victim. But remember: the deeper you go, the closer He becomes...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to reach the end and survive?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the silence of the night, the door creaks... You are an uninvited guest in a house that the owners have long since abandoned. But you are not alone here. A dark silhouette watches from the shadows, following your every step. Who is he? And why does this house not let go of those who cross its threshold?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore rooms full of secrets and terrible finds. Read the notes of the former owner, who tried to drive out the evil, but failed. Solve the riddles to finish what you started - or become the next victim. But remember: the deeper you go, the closer He becomes...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to reach the end and survive?</p>",
